### 知识库专题（v5 §32-44）扩展接口烟测（AppHost 镜像版本）
### AppHost 权威端口 5002；覆盖 jobs/bindings/permissions/versions/retrieval-logs/provider-configs/document-scope parse|index/PUT 全部 stanza。

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5002
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@username = admin
@password = P@ssw0rd!

### 登录
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

###
@accessToken = {{login.response.body.$.data.accessToken}}
@kbId = 1

### -------------------- jobs --------------------

### 列出当前 KB 的所有任务
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge-bases/{{kbId}}/jobs?pageIndex=1&pageSize=20
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 跨 KB 列出全部任务（任务中心）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge-bases/jobs?pageIndex=1&pageSize=50&status=DeadLetter
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 获取任务详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge-bases/{{kbId}}/jobs/1
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 重跑解析（携带 ParsingStrategy）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge-bases/{{kbId}}/jobs/parse
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "documentId": 1,
  "parsingStrategy": {
    "parsingType": 1,
    "extractImage": true,
    "extractTable": true,
    "imageOcr": true
  }
}

### 全量重建索引
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge-bases/{{kbId}}/jobs/rebuild-index
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{}

### 死信重投
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge-bases/{{kbId}}/jobs/1:retry
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 取消任务
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge-bases/{{kbId}}/jobs/2:cancel
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### -------------------- bindings --------------------

### 列出当前 KB 的绑定关系
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge-bases/{{kbId}}/bindings?pageIndex=1&pageSize=50
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 跨 KB 列出全部绑定
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge-bases/bindings?pageIndex=1&pageSize=50
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 新增绑定（Agent / App / Workflow / Chatflow）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge-bases/{{kbId}}/bindings
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "callerType": 0,
  "callerId": "agent_security_assistant",
  "callerName": "安全助手 Agent"
}

### 解除绑定
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge-bases/{{kbId}}/bindings/1
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### -------------------- permissions --------------------

### 列出权限（含 space/project 级继承）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge-bases/{{kbId}}/permissions?pageIndex=1&pageSize=50
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 授权
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge-bases/{{kbId}}/permissions
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "scope": 2,
  "scopeId": "1",
  "knowledgeBaseId": 1,
  "subjectType": 1,
  "subjectId": "role_security_owner",
  "subjectName": "安全负责人",
  "actions": [0, 1, 3, 4, 5]
}

### 撤销
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge-bases/{{kbId}}/permissions/1
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### -------------------- versions --------------------

### 列出版本快照
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge-bases/{{kbId}}/versions?pageIndex=1&pageSize=50
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 创建快照
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge-bases/{{kbId}}/versions
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "label": "v1.0.0",
  "note": "首次发布"
}

### 发布版本
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge-bases/{{kbId}}/versions/1:release
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 回退版本（仅审计标记）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge-bases/{{kbId}}/versions/1:rollback
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 版本对比
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge-bases/{{kbId}}/versions/diff?from=1&to=2
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### -------------------- retrieval (v5 §38) --------------------

### 统一检索（debug=true 返回完整 RetrievalLog）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge-bases/retrieval
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "query": "等保 加密 平台",
  "knowledgeBaseIds": [1],
  "topK": 5,
  "callerContext": {
    "callerType": 0,
    "callerId": "studio-debug",
    "tenantId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
    "userId": "admin"
  },
  "debug": true,
  "retrievalProfile": {
    "topK": 5,
    "minScore": 0,
    "enableRerank": true,
    "enableHybrid": true,
    "weights": { "vector": 0.6, "bm25": 0.4, "table": 0, "image": 0 },
    "enableQueryRewrite": true
  }
}

### 列出某 KB 的检索日志
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge-bases/{{kbId}}/retrieval-logs?pageIndex=1&pageSize=20
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 按 traceId 查询单条日志
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge-bases/retrieval-logs/trc_xxxxxxxx
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### -------------------- table / image views --------------------

### 表格 KB：列定义
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge-bases/{{kbId}}/documents/1/table-columns
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 表格 KB：行视图
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge-bases/{{kbId}}/documents/1/table-rows?pageIndex=1&pageSize=50
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 图片 KB：图片项目（含 caption / ocr / tag 标注）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge-bases/{{kbId}}/documents/1/image-items?pageIndex=1&pageSize=20
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### -------------------- v5 §35 / 计划 G5：document 范围的 parse / index jobs --------------------

### 列出某文档的全部 parse 任务
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge-bases/{{kbId}}/documents/1/parse-jobs
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 重跑解析（document 范围；body 可选）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge-bases/{{kbId}}/documents/1/parse-jobs
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "parsingStrategy": {
    "parsingType": 1,
    "extractImage": true,
    "extractTable": true,
    "imageOcr": true
  }
}

### 列出某文档的全部 index 任务
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge-bases/{{kbId}}/documents/1/index-jobs
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 重建索引（document 范围；append / overwrite）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge-bases/{{kbId}}/documents/1/index-jobs/rebuild
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "chunkingProfile": {
    "mode": 0,
    "size": 512,
    "overlap": 64
  },
  "mode": 1
}

### 死信批量重投（不传 jobIds 时按 KB 全量；可选 type 过滤）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge-bases/{{kbId}}/jobs/dead-letter:retry
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "type": 0
}

### -------------------- 绑定 / 权限 / Provider 写入 --------------------

### 绑定详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge-bases/{{kbId}}/bindings/1
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 权限更新（PUT actions）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge-bases/{{kbId}}/permissions/1
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "actions": [0, 5]
}

### -------------------- provider-configs --------------------

### 获取五类 Provider 配置（upload / storage / vector / embedding / generation）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge-bases/provider-configs
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Upsert provider 配置（路径 role 必须与 body.role 一致）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge-bases/provider-configs/Vector
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "role": 2,
  "providerName": "qdrant",
  "displayName": "Qdrant Cluster (Default)",
  "status": 0,
  "isDefault": true,
  "endpoint": "http://qdrant:6333",
  "region": "cn-east-1",
  "bucketOrIndex": "atlas_kb"
}
